                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14296881" author="tjake" created="Thu, 29 Jan 2015 14:06:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I see in JMX and nodetool cfstats these are all micros.  Even your message above looks like micros...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;What are you expecting to see? and how did you generate the above message?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14296964" author="mike_tr_adamson" created="Thu, 29 Jan 2015 14:57:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The values came from JMC looking at the &amp;lt;cfs&amp;gt;.WriteLatency.Min, &amp;lt;cfs&amp;gt;.WriteLatency. Max and &amp;lt;cfs&amp;gt;.WriteTotalLatency.Count.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If the Min is 315.853 wouldn&apos;t you expect the WriteTotalLatency.Count to be ~340 not 339667? or am I missing something here (likely). &lt;/p&gt;

</comment>
                            <comment id="14296974" author="tjake" created="Thu, 29 Jan 2015 15:06:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You&apos;re right. Attached fix. Please verify&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
